{"tid":157681,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"得返10蚊可以點做？","createTime":"2017-03-15T16:32:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T04:16:59.000Z","uid":16381,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ef4e62b6fdb4f23d732bd42417bb0729b709d626","tid":157681,"uid":16381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T16:32:39.000Z","msg":"平時行街想買10蚊魚蛋食？哼，我教你用10蚊做黨主席。首先係行過馬會，一定要星期六、日，因為咁樣有多啲場次，比你快啲做黨主席。之後就同啲呀姐點點頭就會比你入去。然後大大聲同果呀姐講，「幫我事旦買8串1單雙，10蚊！」，佢就知你係行家，幫你填啲佢唔識嘅賽事。如是者，你就拎住張10蚊嘅8串1。<br />\n<br />\n10蚊買8串1單雙，最少有133倍，中1,330。<br />\n<br />\n再用1330蚊買133條8串1單雙，133倍，總共有176,890蚊。呢個時候已經係17,689倍嘅利潤，做人一定要貪！唔係點做黨主席！<br />\n<br />\n所以當你想收手嘅同時再用果176,890再買17689條8串1單雙，133倍，中23,526,370蚊。呢個時候你心想，都二千幾萬啦喎仲唔夠做？<br />\n<br />\n少年，你肯定睇得連登太少，難道二千幾萬就滿足了麼？所以再用23,526,370過大海，買8場單雙，每場都allin，每場1.95倍，簡稱賭場8串1，淨贏4億9千幾萬。<br />\n<br />\n4億9千幾萬做到幾多次黨主席？我話你聽一次都做唔到！因為你仲未去收購一間爛公司。收購爛公司有乜用？當然係用黎做廠啦。拎間廠去做今時今日最發達嘅野，係咩呀？當然係馬會啦，不過唔可以用馬，因為用馬字開頭會比我呢啲咁醒嘅人贏哂啲錢。所以，一定要叫［林早洩］非有限公司，咁先至抽15%税咋。最後連個「會」字都唔要啦，咁先可以整到啲人。<br />\n<br />\n到時淨係收息我都唔知點計！<br />\n5000蚊先做到黨主席？可笑<br />\n利申:想問下跌左粒魚蛋落應唔應執返黎食"},{"pid":"39fbc61785bd35b2bdf5fb421c51dddc3214197a","tid":157681,"uid":33601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T16:36:30.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52848f9d13adfba173a30f0badfbc89ea79e332b","tid":157681,"uid":5921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T16:39:19.000Z","msg":"8串1實中?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d299fe6269f3934a341343b7aeb6baa3f4eb7d","tid":157681,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T16:40:09.000Z","msg":"幽默感嘅嘢<br />\n算原創<br />\n5/10<br />\n幫你推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b58bdc90dccf9c5a1b4d83696ed54c71b3cdfc6b","tid":157681,"uid":66462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T16:40:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>8串1實中?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真心?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f492f33366280d87343a83fff22c8544be0f16","tid":157681,"uid":11977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T17:55:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幽默感嘅嘢<br />\n算原創<br />\n5/10<br />\n幫你推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n見到第一句黨主席已經唔想睇<br />\n仲原創"},{"pid":"e21a50528a70840fa5784238872409ecc3635330","tid":157681,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T18:04:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9034f4d421af33bfee2e18de3fca569876c78ab6","tid":157681,"uid":24024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T18:45:54.000Z","msg":"幽默感真係無得勉強.."},{"pid":"994077189e9daeeeb53fc592dc91bf047550d770","tid":157681,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T18:46:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cfc1558b61ec94c64f3690dd59adf9e4e978e22a","tid":157681,"uid":43806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T21:41:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幽默感嘅嘢<br />\n算原創<br />\n5/10<br />\n幫你推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n見到第一句黨主席已經唔想睇<br />\n仲原創</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原條撚咩 <br />\n連登真係好撚多賊"},{"pid":"595a1bd12b6ad77b80484ee1a3bfef241f7a3e1c","tid":157681,"uid":33601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T05:32:26.000Z","msg":"摺埋啦"},{"pid":"a07e3ef5ccb59b7018f755a547f16a607d13413e","tid":157681,"uid":8589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T03:24:00.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"0cc84207342c65c1ea1b787ece99edf22ed355a0","tid":157681,"uid":154617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef4e62b6fdb4f23d732bd42417bb0729b709d626","tid":157681,"uid":16381,"like"